### PhotoPipe Function App — Test Requests
### CST8917 Lab 4 | Winter 2026
###
### Usage: Update @baseUrl to your local or deployed Function App URL,
###        then click "Send Request" above each test case.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Test 1: Health Check
### Expected: 200 OK with status "healthy"
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Test 2: Get Processing Results (empty initially)
### Expected: 200 OK with an empty array []
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/get-results

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Test 3: Get Audit Log (empty initially)
### Expected: 200 OK with an empty array []
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

GET {{baseUrl}}/get-audit-log

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Note on Event Grid-triggered functions
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### The process-image and audit-log functions are triggered by Event Grid
### events, not HTTP requests. You cannot test them directly from here.
###
### To test the full pipeline:
### 1. Deploy the Function App to Azure (Part 2)
### 2. Configure Event Grid subscriptions (Part 3)
### 3. Upload an image via the web client or directly to Blob Storage
### 4. Use the get-results and get-audit-log endpoints below to verify
###    that the functions processed the event successfully.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Test 4: Get Results After Upload (run after uploading an image)
### Expected: 200 OK with array of metadata objects
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Update this URL to your deployed function app
# @deployedUrl = https://yourname-photopipe-func.azurewebsites.net/api

# GET {{deployedUrl}}/get-results

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Test 5: Get Audit Log After Upload (run after uploading an image)
### Expected: 200 OK with array of audit entries
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------

# GET {{deployedUrl}}/get-audit-log